Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.81,0:00:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it’s about time \Nyou had more freedom?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You may think you’re ready \Nto be treated as an adult, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.56,0:00:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but do your parents agree?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.35,0:00:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you proven to them \Nthat you can handle more freedom?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, if you want more freedom, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to gain your parents’ trust.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.06,0:00:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Earning their trust takes time.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But every time \Nyou prove yourself responsible, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you get one step closer to your goal.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Some ways you can show \N you are trustworthy are: \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,diligently completing your chores, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,especially without being reminded; \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.23,0:00:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,managing your time wisely \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:00:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and being punctual; \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,taking care of your things; \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,showing that you can handle \Nmoney in a responsible way; \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.44,0:01:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and following through \Non the promises you make.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.69,0:01:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, nobody’s perfect.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you make a mistake, \Nit’s not the end of the world.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.19,0:01:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow the Bible’s advice \Nat Hebrews 13:18 \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.65,0:01:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to conduct yourself \N“honestly in all things.”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the truth \Nand be straightforward. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you admit your mistake \Nand apologize, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,your parents will see \Nthat you are willing \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to take responsibility \Nfor your actions, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.23,0:01:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and they’ll appreciate \Nyour honesty.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.73,0:01:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if you feel \Nthat despite your best efforts, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,your parents still aren’t giving \Nyou enough freedom?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t just get annoyed\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,—talk to them!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Respectfully ask what they think \Nyou need to do to earn their trust.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be surprised \Nto learn of some other areas \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,where you can show \Nyou’re responsible.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,At 2 Corinthians 13:5, \N the Bible says: \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,“Keep proving what you . . . are.”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So you need to build up \Na record of consistency.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That way you’ll prove \Nyou’re worthy of trust.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Every step you take \Nbrings you closer to your goal.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, trust is much harder \Nto gain than it is to lose.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.06,0:02:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But the effort is worth it. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When your parents see you \Nworking hard to earn their trust, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,they will likely be happy \Nto give you more freedom, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and you’ll be another step closer \Nto becoming a responsible adult.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.65,0:00:06.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,自分にはもっと自由があってもいい—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:10.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,もう十分大人だ と思っていますか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:14.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも 親はそう思っているでしょうか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:18.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,もっと自由があっても大丈夫なことを\N親に証明してきましたか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.31,0:00:37.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,そう もっと多くの自由が欲しいなら\N親の信頼を得なければなりません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.23,0:00:40.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,信頼を得るには時間がかかります\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:45.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも 責任ある行動を取るたびに\Nゴールに近づいているのです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:48.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,信頼できることを示すためには—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:52.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,何度も言われなくても\N家の手伝いをきちんとします\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.56,0:00:58.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,自分で上手に時間を管理し\N時間を守りましょう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.23,0:01:03.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,自分の持ち物を大切に扱います\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:06.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,責任をもってお金を管理します\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.60,0:01:11.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,約束したなら守りましょう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:17.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,もちろん 完ぺきな人はいません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.02,0:01:20.10,Default2,,0,0,0,,たとえ失敗しても\N落ち込まないでください\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:23.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,聖書のヘブライ 13章18節に\Nあるように—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.15,0:01:26.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,“すべてのことにおいて正直に”\N行動しましょう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:30.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,本当のことを隠さずに話してください\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:33.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,間違いを認めて謝るなら—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.31,0:01:38.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,親はあなたの責任感や正直さを\N高く評価するでしょう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.15,0:01:39.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,ベストを尽くしているのに—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.69,0:01:43.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,親がなかなか自由を与えてくれないと\N感じるときはどうですか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.27,0:01:46.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,イライラしても 親に話しましょう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:51.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,信頼してもらうために何が必要か\N敬意をもって尋ねてみてください\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:56.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,努力できる意外な点を\N教えてもらえるかもしれません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.06,0:02:02.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,コリント第二 13章5節には—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:06.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,“自分が……どんなものであるかを\N絶えず吟味しなさい”とあります\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:10.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,つまり 信頼の記録を\N積み上げていく必要があるのです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:13.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,信頼できることを証明しましょう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:16.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,一歩一歩 ゴールに近づいて行きます\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:21.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,もちろん 信頼を失うのは簡単ですが\N得るのはとても大変です\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.77,0:02:24.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,それでも 努力する価値があります\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.52,0:02:27.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,親は 信頼を得るために\N努力しているあなたを見て—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.90,0:02:30.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,喜んで もっと自由を与えてくれるでしょう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:47.87,Default2,,0,0,0,,責任ある大人に\Nさらに近づくことができるのです\N
